Field_Binary.name: control_auth_id
Field_Binary.description: Control authority identifier. ; NJPL indicates that the data description information for this SFDU is maintained and disseminated by NASA/JPL.

Field_Binary.name: sfdu_version_id
Field_Binary.description: SFDU label version ID.; 2 indicates that the length attribute field in bytes 12 to 19 is formatted as a binary unsigned integer.

Field_Binary.name: sfdu_class_id
Field_Binary.description: SFDU class ID.; I indicates that this SFDU contains data to be used by an application process.

Field_Binary.name: reserve2
Field_Binary.description: Reserved.; Two bytes.

Field_Binary.name: data_description_id
Field_Binary.description: Data description identifier.; Uniquely identifies the data description information held by the control authority identified in the Control authority identifier item for this type of SFDU.; C123 => Uplink types; C124 => Downlink types; C125 => Derived types; C126 => Interferometric types; C127 => Filtered types

Field_Binary.name: sfdu_length
Field_Binary.description: Length attribute of the tracking data SFDU.; Indicates the length of the data following this element.; DT0 => 162; DT1 => 358 ; DT2 => 194 ; DT3 => 304 ; DT4 => 276 ; DT5 => 388 ; DT6 => 200; DT7 => 330; DT8 => 178 ; DT9 => 124; DT10 => 204 ; DT11 => 182; DT12 => 164 ; DT13 => 160; DT14 => 348; DT15 => 194; DT16 => 182 + 18 * num_obs; DT17 => 194 + 22 * num_obs

Field_Binary.name: chdo_type
Field_Binary.description: Type attribute of the aggregation CHDO.; A value of 1 indicates that this CHDO is an aggregation of CHDOs

Field_Binary.name: chdo_length
Field_Binary.description: Length attribute of the aggregation CHDO.; Indicates the length of the sum of the primary and secondary CHDOs.; CHDO 132 => 78; CHDO 133 => 122; CHDO 134 => 136; CHDO 135 => 100; CHDO 136 => 110

Field_Binary.name: chdo_type
Field_Binary.description: Type attribute of the primary CHDO.; A value of 2 indicates that this CHDO is a primary CHDO.

Field_Binary.name: chdo_length
Field_Binary.description: Length attribute of the primary CHDO. Indicates the length, in bytes, of the value field (bytes after this item) of the primary CHDO.

Field_Binary.name: mjr_data_class
Field_Binary.description: Major data class.; A value of 6 indicates that the data in this SFDU is ground station monitor data.

Field_Binary.name: mnr_data_class
Field_Binary.description: Minor data class.; Indicates data is processed tracking data.

Field_Binary.name: mission_id
Field_Binary.description: Mission ID.

Field_Binary.name: format_code
Field_Binary.description: Format code.; Also referred to as the data type.; 0 => Uplink Carrier Phase; 1 => Downlink Carrier Phase; 2 => Uplink Sequential Ranging Phase; 3 => Downlink Sequential Ranging Phase; 4 => Uplink PN Ranging Phase; 5 => Downlink PN Ranging Phase; 6 => Doppler; 7 => Sequential Ranging; 8 => Angles; 9 => Ramps ; 10 => VLBI; 11 => DRVID ; 12 => Smoothed Noise; 13 => Allan Deviation; 14 => PN Ranging; 15 => Tone Ranging; 16 => Carrier Observable; 17 => Total Phase Observable

Field_Binary.name: chdo_type
Field_Binary.description: Type attribute of the secondary CHDO.

Field_Binary.name: chdo_length
Field_Binary.description: Length attribute of the secondary CHDO. Indicates the length, in bytes, of the value field (bytes after this item) of the secondary CHDO.

Field_Binary.name: orig_id
Field_Binary.description: Originator ID.; Indicates where this SFDU was originated.

Field_Binary.name: last_modifier_id
Field_Binary.description: Last modifier ID.; Indicates where the contents of this SFDU were last modified.

Field_Binary.name: reserve1
Field_Binary.description: Reserved. ; For future expansion of scft_id.

Field_Binary.name: scft_id
Field_Binary.description: Spacecraft number.;

Field_Binary.name: upl_rec_seq_num
Field_Binary.description: Uplink record sequence number (UPL RSN).; This is the record sequence number reported by the uplink subsystem (UPL) equipment.

Field_Binary.name: rec_seq_num
Field_Binary.description: Record sequence number (RSN).; Begins with zero; increments by one for each successive uplink tracking SFDU of the same data type; wraps around from 232-1 to zero. Value is reset to zero when the data processing system software is restarted.

Field_Binary.name: year
Field_Binary.description: Time tag year.

Field_Binary.name: doy
Field_Binary.description: Time tag day of year.

Field_Binary.name: sec
Field_Binary.description: Time tag seconds of day.

Field_Binary.name: rct_day
Field_Binary.description: Record creation time days.; Days since 1/1/1958.

Field_Binary.name: rct_msec
Field_Binary.description: Record creation time milliseconds of day.

Field_Binary.name: ul_dss_id
Field_Binary.description: Uplink antenna number. ;

Field_Binary.name: ul_band
Field_Binary.description: Uplink frequency band.; 0 => Unknown; 1 => S-band; 2 => X-band; 3 => Ka-band; 4 => Ku-band; 5 => L-band

Field_Binary.name: ul_assembly_num
Field_Binary.description: Uplink Assembly Number. ; Note that this is to allow for potential future cases where there might be more than one uplink of the same band at the same antenna.; 0 => Invalid/unknown; 1 => S-/X-band uplink; 2 => Ka-band uplink

Field_Binary.name: transmit_num
Field_Binary.description: Transmitter number. ; Value depends on transmitter used. A value of 0 indicates unknown.

Field_Binary.name: transmit_stat
Field_Binary.description: Transmit status.; 0 => Not transmitting out the horn; 1 => Transmitting out the horn; 2 => Invalid/unknown

Field_Binary.name: transmit_mode
Field_Binary.description: Transmitter mode.; 0 => Low power; 1 => High power; 2 => Invalid/unknown

Field_Binary.name: cmd_modul_stat
Field_Binary.description: Command modulation status.; 0 => OFF; 1 => ON; 2 => Invalid/unknown

Field_Binary.name: rng_modul_stat
Field_Binary.description: Ranging modulation status.; 0 => OFF; 1 => ON; 2 => Invalid/unknown

Field_Binary.name: fts_vld_flag
Field_Binary.description: Frequency and Timing (FTS) validity.; 0 => Equipment is not synced with FTS; 1 => Equipment is synced with FTS

Field_Binary.name: reserve1a
Field_Binary.description: Reserved.; One byte.

Field_Binary.name: transmit_time_tag_delay
Field_Binary.description: Transmit time tag delay. ; Value used to offset uplink time tag (e.g., for Goldstone Beam Waveguide antennas). Value of ?1.0 indicates invalid (or not provided).

Field_Binary.name: ul_zheight_corr
Field_Binary.description: Uplink Z-height correction. ; Value of -99.0 indicates invalid.

Field_Binary.name: mod_day
Field_Binary.description: Modification time days.; Days since 1/1/1958. Last modification time.

Field_Binary.name: mod_msec
Field_Binary.description: Modification time milliseconds of day. ; Last modification time.

Field_Binary.name: version_num
Field_Binary.description: Version number.; Version number of the assembly that generated the data.

Field_Binary.name: sub_version_num
Field_Binary.description: Sub-version number.; Sub-version number of the assembly that generated the data.

Field_Binary.name: sub_sub_version_num
Field_Binary.description: Sub-sub-version number.; Sub-sub-version number of the assembly that generated the data.

Field_Binary.name: reserve1b
Field_Binary.description: Reserved.; One byte.

Field_Binary.name: reserve4
Field_Binary.description: Reserved.; Four bytes.

Field_Binary.name: chdo_type
Field_Binary.description: Type attribute of the uplink sequential ranging phase data CHDO. ; CHDO contains binary data.

Field_Binary.name: chdo_length
Field_Binary.description: Length attribute of the uplink sequential ranging phase data CHDO value field. ; Number of bytes after this item.

Field_Binary.name: stn_cal
Field_Binary.description: Station calibration value. (Two?way). Value includes the equipment in the path, but not the Z?height correction. (0.0 if not measured.)

Field_Binary.name: ul_stn_cal
Field_Binary.description: Uplink station calibration value. ; Value includes the uplink equipment in the path, but not the Z?height correction. (0.0 if not measured.)

Field_Binary.name: ul_cal_freq
Field_Binary.description: Uplink calibration frequency. Frequency at which the calibration was done.

Field_Binary.name: cal_std_dev
Field_Binary.description: Standard deviation of station calibration value.; For stn_cal and ul_stn_cal.

Field_Binary.name: cal_pts
Field_Binary.description: Calibration points. ; Number of measurements made in computing station calibration values (stn_cal, ul_stn_cal, cal_std_dev).

Field_Binary.name: ul_rng_phs
Field_Binary.description: Measured range phase.; Range phase.

Field_Binary.name: transmit_switch_stat
Field_Binary.description: Transmitter switch status.; 0 => Antenna; 1 => Water load; 2 => Invalid/unknown

Field_Binary.name: invert
Field_Binary.description: Invert. ; Polarity of modulation.; 0 => Not inverted; 1 => Inverted

Field_Binary.name: transmit_op_pwr
Field_Binary.description: Transmitter output power.

Field_Binary.name: template_id
Field_Binary.description: Template ID. ; Ranging configuration file ID, or the name of the PN pattern

Field_Binary.name: t1
Field_Binary.description: T1 setting.

Field_Binary.name: t2
Field_Binary.description: T2 setting.

Field_Binary.name: t3
Field_Binary.description: T3 setting.

Field_Binary.name: first_comp_num
Field_Binary.description: First component number.

Field_Binary.name: last_comp_num
Field_Binary.description: Last component number.

Field_Binary.name: chop_comp_num
Field_Binary.description: Chop component number.; This is the component used to chop the other components.

Field_Binary.name: num_drvid
Field_Binary.description: Number of DRVID measurements.

Field_Binary.name: transmit_inphs_time_year
Field_Binary.description: Transmit In-phase time year.; Year of the time of zero phase on uplink range generation.

Field_Binary.name: transmit_inphs_time_doy
Field_Binary.description: Transmit In-phase time day of year.; Day of year of the time of zero phase on uplink range generation.

Field_Binary.name: transmit_inphs_time_sec
Field_Binary.description: Transmit In-phase time seconds of day.; Seconds of day of the time of zero phase on uplink range generation.

Field_Binary.name: carr_sup_rng_modul
Field_Binary.description: Carrier Suppression by ranging modulation.; Reduction in carrier power due to ranging modulation.

Field_Binary.name: rng_modul_amp
Field_Binary.description: Ranging modulation amplitude.; Actual digital modulation amplitude used by the ranging hardware.

Field_Binary.name: exc_scalar_num
Field_Binary.description: Exciter Scalar Numerator.; Numerator of ratio between ranging reference signal and uplink sky frequency.

Field_Binary.name: exc_scalar_den
Field_Binary.description: Exciter Scalar Denominator.; Denominator of ratio between ranging reference signal and uplink sky frequency.

Field_Binary.name: rng_cycle_time
Field_Binary.description: Ranging cycle time.; Time to complete one cycle of the ranging code.

Field_Binary.name: time_tag_corr_flag
Field_Binary.description: Time tag correction flag.; Indicates results of validation of the block time tag.; 0 => No validation attempted; 1 => Validated, no change; 2 => Validated, changed

Field_Binary.name: type_time_corr_flag
Field_Binary.description: Type of time tag correction flag.; Indicates what type of time tag correction was made.; 0 => No correction; 1 => Year correction; 2 => DOY correction; 3 => Both Year and DOY correction

Field_Binary.name: clock_waveform
Field_Binary.description: Clock waveform type.; 0 => Squarewave; 1 => Sinewave

Field_Binary.name: chop_start_num
Field_Binary.description: Chop Start.; The first component chopped.

Field_Binary.name: rng_meas_type
Field_Binary.description: Range Measurement Type.; Type of sequential measurement.; 0 => Ranging Round Trip; 1 => Calibration; 2 => Telemetry-Based Ranging; 3 => 1-way to Spacecraft; 4 => 1-way from Spacecraft; 5 => Coupled Noncoherent

Field_Binary.name: fabricated_sfdu_flag
Field_Binary.description: Fabricated SFDU Flag; Indicates whether this SFDU was artificially fabricated in support of 3-way ranging.; 0 => Originally generated by UPL and validated by TTC software; 1 => Fabricated by TTC software

Field_Binary.name: reserve6
Field_Binary.description: Reserved.; Six bytes.
